articles.title: MTG and Rand Paul float Elon Musk for speaker of the House
articles.description: House Speaker Mike Johnson is facing major unrest among his colleagues after Musk and Trump tanked a bipartisan deal to avoid a government shutdown.

articles.title: Some Amazon warehouse workers are striking. The company says it isn't affecting holiday deliveries.
articles.description: Some Amazon warehouse workers walked out at several fulfillment centers Thursday. Amazon says it's not seeing holiday delivery effects.

articles.title: FAA bans drone flights in much of New Jersey
articles.description: The 22 flight restrictions are in effect through January 17 for much of the state of New Jersey.
